{"tid":896772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"職場借錢唔還概玩法（附圖）","createTime":"2018-11-10T10:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T12:29:36.000Z","uid":197926,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0e316c9604f884a1b6515e909911ed273e882f","tid":896772,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"陳幾何時，轉左工，有個同事叫聚舊食飯，之後借左我錢，轉左公司冇點見，過左一星期都知未還就WhatsApp 佢，唔覆。電話又唔聽。Block9埋我，當跌撚左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n追還錢前：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onWgPLZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonWgPLZ.png&h=7227f89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n追還錢後：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qTUVkSF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTUVkSF.png&h=2f89c037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最近又收到佢訊息，話好撚掛著我，要約我出泥食飯。呢d人係咪有問題？好撚嘔心 我reply叫佢還錢，當然最後冇還到，之後又再block 多次。<br />\n<br />\n好心佢啦，初出泥做野先俾佢昆，年紀大過我，做人唔好甘撚柒。<br />\n我捐左佢都好撚過，買六合彩都起麻有個機會。唔搵我，我都唔記得左，突然收到呢d msg, 真係把撚火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。記得呢條仆街屋企係有錢，但成鳩日唔帶提款卡，只帶現金，周圍同我度水。世界真係咩撚野人都有。🤮<br />\n<br />\n利申：4個位<br />\n<br />\n巴打們，俾你係我，你會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dab6f4264491e61bd7389a80138117c90e7f0a","tid":896772,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"有得點姐 當買個教訓囉"},{"pid":"fa45f9b3752361ec3e9f36175adc04783038c48c","tid":896772,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"借錢俾人嗰位on9啲"},{"pid":"ae9f8154268ff13da6c6d239a2e02a60aa10e073","tid":896772,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"Btw 泥你老母"},{"pid":"6ef28b8f2bc2d8cd1d97b7939cdae5e2e3bc61f2","tid":896772,"uid":192017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"同佢扮返friend，問哂佢住邊